704701f-a.title: Brooklyn: Greene Avenue - Wilson Avenue
704701f-a.text:
(1)
Greene Ave., east side, north from the N.E. corner of Wilson Ave.
The view in the foreground, is the Amer. Brewery Hall. The large
building is the North American Brewing Ce.
September 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from another angle.
September 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
